00:36:45.800 --> 00:36:46.840
Esperaré tu respuesta entonces.

00:36:47.920 --> 00:36:48.320
Está bien.

00:36:52.360 --> 00:36:52.880
Amy,

00:36:53.190 --> 00:36:53.800
